⚠ ESTE JUEGO ES UNA PRUEBA BETA, ¡HABRÁ ERRORES! ⚠

Esto es solo una prueba beta (sí, tuve que decirlo dos veces) del primer mundo para "I Wanna Be The Bloxxer"," que se basa en un juego llamado "I Wanna Be The Guy"." Este NO es el juego completo, ya que todavía se está desarrollando (por eso algunos elementos en el escenario NO funcionan). Personas a las que no les gustó = Noobs apestosos que no pueden git gud.

---CONTROLS---
Pulsa dos veces para saltar dos veces
Presiona el botón R o 'Retry' para reiniciar
Presiona Z o agáchate para guardar en una estación de guardado
Agáchate justo antes de que te golpeen para realizar una parada

Presiona Q y E para equipar / desequipar (utilizado para enemigos, mini jefes y peleas de jefes) Plataforma soportada: PC Mobile Console

Access available for purchase in-game!

FAQ

Q: If I purchased paid access before, will I need to pay again?
A: Nope! You'll just be able to play.

Q: If I purchase the alpha, will I need to buy the beta too?
A: Nope, the beta will be free!

Q: When does the open beta come out?
A: We aren't sure yet! It's a ways out, but we'll update you when we have news.

Q: Is there wallclimb boosting?
A: Yes.

Climb your way out of a deep pit with your friend in this obby game. The pit is unforgiving and the climb is tough, but you’re not alone. You and your friend are attached via an elastic rope that will test your teamwork and coordination. Learn how to use the rope to your advantage and overcome the challenges of being dependent on each other. Can you make it to the top?

How to start:
 - Go up to someone you'd like to pair up with.
 - Press the "Request rope" button.
 - To accept a request simply go up a requesting person and request a rope back.
 - You're set, have fun!

⛰️ Current maximum altitude: 400 M
